ACEM is a member of IMMA (International Motorcycle Manufacturers Association).&#xd;
ACEM is a member of FAS (Forum for the Automobile and Society), MPE (Mobility for Prosperity in Europe) and MCC (MotorCycle Community in Europe).&#xd;
